# Manufacturing Industry Rules (制造业行业规则)

Scope: manufacturing-pack and related AppPacks

## Domain Knowledge

- Core entities: Machine, ProductionLine, WorkOrder, Product, QualityInspection, Material, Inventory, Maintenance, Shift, Operator.
- Key metrics: OEE (Overall Equipment Effectiveness), cycle time, scrap rate, MTBF (Mean Time Between Failures), MTTR (Mean Time To Repair), inventory turnover.
- Data sources: MES, SCADA/PLC (OPC-UA), ERP, WMS (仓储管理), QMS.

## Data Characteristics

- SCADA/PLC data: high-frequency time-series (sub-second intervals), stored in ClickHouse.
- OPC-UA integration via dts-data-connector OPC-UA adapter.
- Data volume: single production line can generate 10M+ records/day.

## Safety Constraints

- Machine start/stop commands are risk_level: high → mandatory HITL approval.
- Quality hold/release decisions require QA manager approval.
- AI-driven production scheduling changes are ADVISORY — production manager confirms.

## Data Security

- Production process parameters: CONFIDENTIAL (trade secrets).
- Quality inspection raw data: INTERNAL.
- Inventory levels: CONFIDENTIAL (competitive intelligence).
